  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-based climbing game</h2><br>Balance Knight is a game in which the player must advance up a scaffolding shaken by physics.The only controls are moving and jumping. <br>But it will take some time to get used to the wobbly scaffolding.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>The objective of the game is only to go up.<br>Move through the wobbly scaffolding shaken by physics to reach the goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hard Game</h2><br>Don't give up if you fall.Next time you will be able to climb.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wobbly scaffold shaken by physics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>When you step on the scaffold, it starts moving by your weight.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It looks easy, but it's hard.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hard, but it's fun.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics-based climbing game</h2><br>Balance Knight is a game in which the player must advance up a scaffolding shaken by physics.The only controls are moving and jumping. <br>But it will take some time to get used to the wobbly scaffolding.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>The objective of the game is only to go up.<br>Move through the wobbly scaffolding shaken by physics to reach the goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/8b16991a42776794e30131a81b696a31.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hard Game</h2><br>Don't give up if you fall.Next time you will be able to climb.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/f6757c2a16292b47e990ed76ed0a002e.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Wobbly scaffold shaken by physics.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>When you step on the scaffold, it starts moving by your weight.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>It looks easy, but it's hard.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hard, but it's fun.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.poster.avif?t=1655190692\" width=600 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.webm?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1959440/extras/c7652f75afde87f1f0c4b41fa5051f8a.mp4?t=1655190692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
